snippet.title: Predecessor Playstation Closed Beta | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Predecessor is coming to Playstation for a Closed Beta on 5th December 2023! Sign up to the Predecessor Closed Beta on our website and refer your friends!

Sign up here:
http://playp.red/oHx450Q6Y6E

▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰

Play Predecessor now on Steam and Epic!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/961200/Predecessor/ 

Epic Games: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/predecessor 

▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰

Follow us on social for more!

💬 Discord: https://discord.gg/Predecessor 

📱 Tiktok: https://tinyurl.com/playpredTok
